{
  "texts": [
    "To do so, we used another site foot_11 created exclusively for this index.",
    "Grammarly foot_12 was used to count the number of spelling and grammar mistakes in the stimuli.",
    "Before use, Grammarly first asks what the objectives are in terms of audience, formality, and intent.",
    "To better align Grammarly to the other readability scores used in this study, the target audience was set in Grammarly's default settings.",
    "The default audience is \"knowledgeable\" and the tool focuses on reading and comprehension."
  ]
}